{
  "stem": "895.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He had one son who was a well-known saxophonist.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He had a contract to play in-- play in England, but the war broke out and he couldn't come.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He died in the intern camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They didn't torture him in the intern camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "He died of a sickness.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I can tell you what the sickness was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "He was a guy who went out with all  the women-- syphilis.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "He died.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "He was-- Max, he, he was about 22.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But he thought he still a daughter living and that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "So when he went back to Glasgow, he committed suicide in a park in Glasgow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "His wife lived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "She, she just died.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "She lived in Amsterdam-- his second wife.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "The first wife, she died when my daughter was-- my wife was 12 years old.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So I didn't know her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And that was the end of my father-in-law.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I never saw him again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Then I heard he, he commit suicide.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, she got back a license to start the textile again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we went in the south of Amsterdam, an empty shop-- it was hard to get-- on the corner, Columbus Street.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the name of her father's shops was the Blauwe Winkels-- the Blue Shops.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was well known in Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we opened the shop.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I have a photo with my little baby, Daniel, standing in front.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went in the textile business.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we got textile.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we opened it, 200 people standing outside there because, you know, there was all-- couldn't get no shirts, that time, at all.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They bought a lot-- emptied.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I got a-- we had that shop for about 12 years.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
